laboratory_examinations.findings: A single metastasis in the right frontoparietal region, which measures 1.6 x 2.1 cm, smaller than the prior examination (3.5 x 3.5 cm). Lesser degree of surrounding vasogenic edema. No new metastases identified.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: The metastasis decreased in size from 3.5 x 3.5 cm to 1.6 x 2.1 cm.
